twodtree

Class Queue

  • java.lang.Object
    • twodtree.Queue

  • public class Queue
extends java.lang.Object
    This class is a linked list implementation of the queue with a front and rear pointer. It has a node of SingleNode type. It is used in the level order and reverse ordere traversal
